The Soviets had a suspected facility at Lakhta near St Petersburg, and a P4
hood line at the Institute of Dangerous Pathogens at Minsk.
The Swedes are building one at the Institute for Infection Control at Solna.
--
Peter Lowry MD
SAIC
Joppa Md.
